text: VETRIZO TECHNOLOGIES Empowering Ideas with Code Company Overview: Vetrizo Technologies is a cutting-edge software development and AI consulting company based in San Francisco, California. We specialize in building custom digital products and intelligent systems for startups, enterprises, and government agencies. Our mission is to transform business ideas into robust, scalable, and innovative solutions. Founded: 2023 Employees: 28 Headquarters: San Francisco, CA CEO: Abdul Ahad CTO: Hammad Jhujh Website: www.vetrizo.com Email: hello@vetrizo.com Services: - Custom Web & Mobile App Development - AI/ML Model Development - Data Analytics & Business Intelligence - Cloud Infrastructure & DevOps - Product Design (UI/UX) Clients & Industries: We’ve worked with clients across fintech, healthtech, logistics, and education sectors. Notable collaborations include: - Ahsan Enterprises (US) - MedixFlow Health - EduBridge AI Labs Technologies: - Frontend: React, Flutter, TailwindCSS - Backend: Node.js, Python, Django, FastAPI - Databases: PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis - ML Stack: PyTorch, TensorFlow, LangChain, Hugging Face - Infrastructure: AWS, Docker, GitHub Actions Recent Projects: 1. **DocAI** – An intelligent document classifier using transformer-based models. 2. **TradeScope** – A predictive trading engine for short-term equity strategies. 3. **SafeBox** – A secure personal data vault with integrated BigID compliance. Vision: To become a global leader in applied
AI solutions that are simple, ethical, and high-impact. Values: - Innovation through experimentation - Transparency and trust - People-first mindset
